snippet.title: Dream Cage - Exclusive Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Get a look at some creepy first-person gameplay from Dream Cage, the upcoming horror game that puts you in the shoes of a 50-year-old insomniac struggling with sleep paralysis who must grapple with his fears realized before his eyes over five terrifying nights. 

Wishlist it on Steam if you're interested: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3122170/Dream_Cage/ 

#DreamCage #Gaming #IGN
